<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.9">
<l>paṟṟē loṉṟumilēṉ pāvamēceytu pāviyāṉēṉ</l>
<l>maṟṟē loṉṟaṟiyēṉ māyaṉēyeṅkaḷ mātavaṉē</l>
<l>kaṟtēṉ pāyntoḻukuṅ kamalaccuṉai vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>vaṟṟēṉ vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I reach out, I do not have anything [to support me];</l>
<l rend="indent">committing only sins, I have become a sinner.</l>
<l>I do not know any other relief, Māyaṉ, our Mādhava.</l>
<l>You of Vēṅkaṭa with lotus ponds where mountain honey runs and drips,</l>
<l>I, who was ruined, came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
